  <brief_title>Safety/Tolerability and Efficacy of YHD001 in Patients With Acute and Chronic Bronchitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo/Active-controlled, Multi-center, Phase 3 Clinical Trial to Investigate the Safety/Tolerability and Efficacy of YHD001 After Oral Administration in Patients With Acute or Chronic Bronchitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
