  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will conduct with 4 comparative groups orally treated with YHD001 dose level
      1(t.i.d.), YHD001 dose level 2(t.i.d.), pelargonium sidoides extract 9mL(t.i.d.) or Placebo
      for 7 days.

      The treatments will be assigned randomly to patients (n=116) with acute or chronic
      bronchitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The outcome measures is to evaluate the overall change from baseline to the end of treatment
      in scores relating to the severity of four symptom of bronchitis: cough, sputum, QOL of daily
      life, QOL of falling asleep at night.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
